## ğŸ”§ Install & Setup Splunk

1ï¸âƒ£ Install dependencies:  
`apt update && apt install -y wget`

2ï¸âƒ£ Download & install Splunk:  
`wget -O splunk.deb https://download.splunk.com/products/splunk/releases/9.0.5/linux/splunk-9.0.5.deb`  
`dpkg -i splunk.deb`  
`/opt/splunk/bin/splunk start --accept-license --answer-yes`

3ï¸âƒ£ Access Splunk WebUI:  
`http://192.168.99.30:8000` (login: `admin / changeme`)

4ï¸âƒ£ Configure data inputs:  
- **UDP 514** (for pfSense logs):  
  `Settings > Data Inputs > Add Data > UDP 514`
- **Windows Event Logs** (via Splunk Universal Forwarder)
- **Samba Logs** (via syslog)

